I'm a new technologies enthusiast and I spent many of my free time to learn and investigate new trends. I am proficient in many programming languages, environments, and operating systems, and can pick up new ones in the blink of an eye.

I'm looking for a freelance position. Permanent, Full Time, or a 1 year contract minimum.

larquin.name: Micah Adams
larquin.bio:
Lead Software Engineer & Software Architect at The Canton Group (http://www.cantongroup.com), a Baltimore based company that offers a variety of technology services to clients in the Mid-Atlantic Area. 

I have considerable experience in software development where it applies specifically to supporting Informatics research, Bio-informatics, and Imaging Informatics. 

I worked on a variety of NIBIB, NIST, and NIH funded projects to improve information systems for healthcare. 

My interests include functional programming, AI and Computational Intelligence, concurrency, natural language processing, data ontologies, LISP, Clojure, Ruby and JavaScript.
